MIMA LARP is a Live Action Role Play to play with an AI chat bot called MIMA.
To play the LARP you must start by creating a simple character (see bottom left) and then read each text in the chapter wheel; moving forwards at your own pace.
Each chapter has suggested questions for you to ask Mima. At the end of each chapter turn over and spin the happening wheel to have a situation.
You can play alone or with a group of friends.
